istory of Michigan | url= |date=1915|publisher= Lewis Publishing Company |quote= }}\n\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last= Stern|first= Daniel|title= The American Artisan and Hardware Record: Volume 79, No. 1 | url= |date=1920a|publisher= Daniel Stern |quote= }}\n\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last= Taylor|first= Henry|title= Compendium of History of City of Detroit | url= |date=1909|publisher= Henry Taylor & Company |quote= }}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dwyer, Jeremiah}}\n[[Category:Businesspeople from Detroit]]\n[[Category:1837 births]]\n[[Category:1920 deaths]]\n[[Category:Businesspeople from Brooklyn]]\n[[Category:Michigan Democrats]]\n", "name_user": "PohranicniStraze", "label": "safe", "comment": "sp", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremiah_Dwyer"}
