 Serie A|2019\u201320]]\n|6||1||1||0||0||0||7||1\n|-\n!Total\n!24!!3!!3!!0!!0!!0!!27!!3\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|'''Career Total'''\n!424!!37!!45!!2!!54!!3!!523!!42\n|}\n\n=== International ===\n{{updated|5 March 2014}}<ref name=SW/><ref name=\"FIGC\">{{cite web|url=http://www.figc.it/nazionali/DettaglioConvocato?codiceConvocato=2066&squadra=1|title=Nazionale in cifre \u2013 FIGC: Maggio, Christian|website=figc.it|publisher=FIGC|language=Italian|accessdate=17 April 2015}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | [[Italy national football team|Italy national team]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2008||1||0\n|-\n|2009||1||0\n|-\n|2010||4||0\n|-\n|2011||8||0\n|-\n|2012||8||0\n|-\n|2013||11||0\n|-\n|2014||1||0\n|-\n!Total||34||0\n|}\n\n== Honours ==\n\n=== Club ===\n;Napoli<ref name=SW>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/christian-maggio/4147/|title=C. Maggio|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=17 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Coppa Italia]] (2): [[2011\u201312 Coppa Italia|2011\u201312]], [[2013\u201314 Coppa Italia|2013\u201314]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]] (1): [[2014 Supercoppa Italiana|2014]]\n\n=== International ===\n;Italy<ref name=SW/>\n*[[UEFA European Championship]]: Runner-up [[UEFA Euro 2012|2012]]\n*[[FIFA Confederations Cup]]: Third Place [[FIFA Confederations Cup|2013]]\n\n=== Individual ===\n*[[Oscar del Calcio]] - [[Serie A Team of the Year]] (3): 2010\u201311,<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aia-figc.it/dettaglio.asp?ID=6050 |title=Gran Cala' del Calcio 2011: Rizzoli premiato miglior arbitro |publisher=FIGC.it |language=Italian |date=24 January 2012 |accessdate=21 June 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103212125/http://aia-figc.it/dettaglio.asp?ID=6050 |archivedate=3 November 2013 |df=dmy }}</ref> 2011\u201312,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/serie_a/2013/01/27-242192/Gran+Gal%26%23224%3B+del+Calcio+Aic.+E%26apos%3B+Pirlo+il+migliore+del+2012|title=Gran Gal\u00e0 del Ca